                                    The Nurse Generalist
                              

                A BSN degree from UIC will provide you with the strongest possible foundation for a fulfilling career as a nurse
              





            BSN programs
          










                            The traditional program
                    

                The on-campus BSN program is the classic college experience
            












                            The completion program
                    

                Our fully online RN to BSN program is perfect for working nurses taking the next step
            











                                    The Career Changer
                              

                For people with a bachelor’s degree in a non-nursing ﬁeld who wish to join the growing and gratifying field of nursing
              





            Grad-entry MS
          










                            About the program
                    

                Ranked #19 in the nation, our MS program is among the best in the Midwest
            












                            Unbeatable support
                    

                Our Clinical Learning Resource Center has everything you need to succeed
            











                                    The Clinical Leader
                              

                Graduates enrich their clinical skills and develop leadership skills, preparing for elevated roles as care coordinators
              





            Tiles
          










                            About the program
                    

                Ranked #19 in the nation, our MS program is among the best in the Midwest
            












                            RN without a bachelor's in nursing? No problem.
                    

                Our AGMS Transition Program is for RNs with non-nursing bachelor's degrees
            











                                    The Expert Clinician
                              

                DNP students graduate with an exceptional blend of clinical, organizational, financial and leadership skills
              





            Tiles
          










                            About the program
                    

