                            Choose one of our 12 focus areas
                    

                Preparing APRNs and healthcare leaders
            











                                    The Nurse Researcher
                              

                Our program emphasizes strong mentoring relationships between students and advisors from our world-class faculty
              





            Tiles
          










                            About the program
                    

                Join a research community with five Hall of Fame researchers and 29 AAN fellows
            












                            Researchers work in every aspect of health
                    

                Find faculty in your area of research interest
            











                                    The Lifelong Learner
                              

                When a full degree isn't what you're seeking, certificate programs offer an increased level of specialized skill
              





